{"tid":2188846,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[s][size=2]休班[/size=2][/s]警察涉協助管理賭檔　控罪書無提職業　指欲聘大狀身在英國　官准月底答辯","createTime":"2020-09-04T13:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T05:10:16.000Z","uid":359022,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"716421e33349fbed5cebb3fd4a59199eed7c72e9","tid":2188846,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/休班警涉協助管理賭檔-控罪書無提職業-指欲聘大狀身在英國-官准月底答辯/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%B6%89%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%B3%AD%E6%AA%94-%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA%E6%9B%B8%E7%84%A1%E6%8F%90%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD-%E6%8C%87%E6%AC%B2%E8%81%98%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E8%BA%AB%E5%9C%A8%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-%E5%AE%98%E5%87%86%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E7%AD%94%E8%BE%AF%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cVSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=b63ade78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%B6%89%E5%8D%94%E5%8A%A9%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E8%B3%AD%E6%AA%94-%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA%E6%9B%B8%E7%84%A1%E6%8F%90%E8%81%B7%E6%A5%AD-%E6%8C%87%E6%AC%B2%E8%81%98%E5%A4%A7%E7%8B%80%E8%BA%AB%E5%9C%A8%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-%E5%AE%98%E5%87%86%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E7%AD%94%E8%BE%AF%2F&h=3013fcc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/休班警涉協助管理賭檔-控罪書無提職業-指欲聘大狀身在英國-官准月底答辯/</a><br />\n<br />\n<del><span class=\"small\">休班</span></del>警察涉協助管理賭檔　控罪書無提職業　指欲聘大狀身在英國　官准月底答辯<br />\n<br />\n警方在今年 5 月突擊搜查屯門恒威工業大廈一個 Party Room 單位，搗破一個非法賭博場所，期間拘捕兩名<del><span class=\"small\">休班</span></del>警員。33 歲警員因證據不足，獲無條件釋放；52 歲警員被控一項協助管理賭場罪，惟其<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">控罪書上無報稱職業</span></strong></span>，今（4 日）在屯門裁判法院提堂。警員希望押後更長時間，指其<span class=\"red\">欲聘請的大律師仍在英國</span>，如回港需要隔離 14 天。裁判官張潔宜則指，已給予他 4 星期諮詢法律意見，案件押至 9 月 30 日答辯，被告以原有條件保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被告為潘藝志（52歲），控罪書上無報稱職業，被控一項協助管理賭場罪。控罪指，他在今年 5 月 4 日，在屯門建泰街恒威工業大廈 15 樓 2 室直接管理賭場。裁判官張潔宜批准案件押後 4 星期答辯，以候被告聘請律師及索取法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n同場其他9人 罰款500<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚴正執法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />限聚令非法賭檔不受規限<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蛇王辦案 搞9同僚洗你教<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撤控警又贏 500呢？"},{"pid":"e45e32f3cf930975cdaaa1082f2d38468ce0f009","tid":2188846,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"c1b1f14290c4e43d6ab513a6b1ae40630f5b6745","tid":2188846,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"85bd59aad9aedcf608a35f60082289677b5d1d57","tid":2188846,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:15:07.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"332ef36eb1f367de977ceb62b20110fe66226dfa","tid":2188846,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:15:18.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5e06705b32292d60d738764ba0d99ecc90ab459c","tid":2188846,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:15:21.000Z","msg":"醜聞日日有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82f1fbc40bb48934ab3209915b07826802af919","tid":2188846,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:15:28.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"afd12797a72c22cff468759601151dd14a7814bb","tid":2188846,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:15:43.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"909cafd11b5213eff2984afbfa4dcfd8b04d0b47","tid":2188846,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ee4652a4103be707e4d415237305e5455f7f9b94","tid":2188846,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T13:15:58.000Z","msg":"